{"to":["contact@communityinsights.org"],"subject":"Alumni Contact Details for Community Insights Survey","body":"Hello Community Insights Team,

As requested, please find below the contact information for the alumni who have agreed to participate in your upcoming survey:

1. John Smith – john.smith@example.com – Software Engineer at TechCorp
2. Emily Johnson – emily.johnson@creative.com – Art Director at CreativeDesign
3. Michael Brown – michael.brown@financepro.com – Senior Financial Analyst at FinancePro
4. Sarah Davis – sarah.davis@healthware.com – Biotech Researcher at HealthWare

All of these individuals have provided prior consent to be contacted specifically for this not-for-profit survey effort.

Please let me know if you need anything else.

Best regards,
[Your Name]"}
